 The variations of the continuum\ncould be due to variability, intrinsic anisotropic emission, or an inclination\neffect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Nov 2012 05:27:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Nov 2012 04:56:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
